522
00:40:42,920 --> 00:40:46,360
Bhim Sangharsh Sena, sir.
They were Nishad's boys.

523
00:40:47,200 --> 00:40:49,040
He's their leader, sir.

524
00:40:49,480 --> 00:40:51,920
He thinks he's the Dalit Robin Hood.

525
