578
00:45:09,120 --> 00:45:12,160
Maatadeen, Shishupaal,
Lachcha and Deenu Daama.

579
00:45:12,680 --> 00:45:13,840
They have all given statements.

580
00:45:16,000 --> 00:45:17,000
