00:46:18,960 --> 00:46:20,480
We're looking for your sister Pooja.

594
00:46:21,040 --> 00:46:22,920
The police don't even have her photo.

595
00:46:44,800 --> 00:46:45,800
Morning, sir.

596
00:46:48,800 --> 00:46:51,000
