Nishad has stopped the men
from his caste from working.

689
00:54:12,440 --> 00:54:13,600
They've alerted everyone on WhatsApp.

690
00:54:23,800 --> 00:54:25,600
You and I are invisible to them.

691
00:54:26,280 --> 00:54:28,440
